{NORTH definitely does NOT have a balanced hand. She has two doubletons and a 
6-card Club suit. 

But she DOES have 18 points, (two extra for the fifth and sixth Clubs), and her 18 added to 
SOUTH's minimum of 15 is enough to bid 6NT.

Notice how easy this will be to play once that Club suit is established.}

